  "SubGoals": [],
  "Description": "The BuildStep goal processes a build step by checking if it has changed since the last execution. If the hash of the current step matches the previous hash, it skips the step. Otherwise, it reads a prompt from a file, sends it to a language model, and processes the result to extract method name, parameters, and return variable.",
